OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,FMilitary families in Scotland are to
OL,7,Freceive additional childcare support
OL,8,Fworth up to #6,000 per year under a UK
OL,9,FGovernment scheme designed to close
OL,10,Fthe "big gap" in childcare provision
OL,11,Fbetween England and Scotland.
OL,13,FThe initiative, which will begin in
OL,14,FSeptember 2026, will see UK armed
OL,15,Fforces families in Scotland reimbursed
OL,16,Ffor up to 30 hours of childcare per
OL,17,Fweek for children aged between nine
OL,18,Fmonths and three years.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
