FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) said the
OL,7,Fscheme will save eligible military
OL,8,Ffamilies in Scotland up to #6,000 per
OL,9,Fchild per year, and ensure they get
OL,10,Fthe same Government-funded childcare
OL,11,Fsupport as forces families in England.
OL,13,FAnnouncing the scheme during a visit
OL,14,Fto Dreghorn Barracks in Edinburgh on
OL,15,FThursday, UK Defence Secretary John
OL,16,FHealey said "it is right" military
OL,17,Ffamilies get the childcare support
OL,18,Fthey need wherever they are posted.
OL,26,@xD@MOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,F"I don't want forces families paying a
OL,7,Fpenalty for serving in Scotland, and
OL,8,Fthere's a big gap in the help for
OL,9,Fchildcare costs for those serving in
OL,10,FEngland to the big gap that the
OL,11,FScottish Government leaves in
OL,12,FScotland," he said.
OL,14,F"So, I'm here to confirm that we will
OL,15,Fmatch the support in England.
OL,17,F"That means we'll cover the cost of 30
OL,18,Fhours of childcare for children of
OL,19,Fworking parents between the age of
OL,20,Fnine months until they hit their third
OL,21,Fbirthday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]vD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,F"It gives them extra options. It means
OL,7,Fparents can have a choice of serving
OL,8,Fand living in Scotland and bringing up
OL,9,Ftheir family here, which for some is
OL,10,Fmade so much harder at the moment by
OL,11,Fthe Scottish Government's failure."
OL,13,FHe said in England all working
OL,14,Ffamilies with children aged between
OL,15,Fnine months and three years get 30
OL,16,Fhours per week free childcare ` but
OL,17,Fthat north of the border "this
OL,18,FScottish nationalist government does
OL,19,Fnot do that".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cO]yD@ZOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,F"We can't solve the problem for all
OL,7,FScots families, but I can solve the
OL,8,Fproblem for those forces families that
OL,9,Fsupport those who serve in uniform,
OL,10,Fand that's what I'm announcing today,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,F"So, from September, the start of the
OL,14,Fnew academic year, that support will
OL,15,Fbe in place just as it is for England,
OL,16,Ffor any families that are serving here
OL,17,Fin Scotland."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]uD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
