FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,FAs well as matching childcare support
OL,7,Fin England, the MoD also said the
OL,8,Fscheme is a "major step" in the
OL,9,Fdelivery of its pledge to renew the
OL,10,FUK's contract with its armed forces.
OL,12,FIt added that childcare is cited as
OL,13,Fone of several factors affecting Armed
OL,14,FForces retention and morale, and that
OL,15,Faddressing it is part of the
OL,16,Fgovernment's "mission" to fix the
OL,17,Frecruitment crisis.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@XO]xD@NOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,FScottish Secretary Douglas Alexander
OL,7,Fsaid: "The UK Government is renewing
OL,8,Fthe country's contract with our
OL,9,Fmilitary personnel, and this latest
OL,10,Fscheme will be transformative in
OL,11,Fhelping tackle the cost of living for
OL,12,Fhundreds of Armed Forces families in
OL,13,FScotland.
OL,15,F"It is vital that those who serve `
OL,16,Fand have served ` in the military and
OL,17,Ftheir families receive fair treatment.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,F"In addition to this latest measure `
OL,7,Fsaving up to #6,000 per year in
OL,8,Fchildcare costs for each child ` we
OL,9,Fhave introduced a new housing strategy
OL,10,Fwhich will make homes fit for heroes,
OL,11,Fdelivered the biggest pay rise for
OL,12,Fpersonnel in 20 years and put the
OL,13,FArmed Forces Covenant into law.
OL,15,F"Scotland plays such a vital role in
OL,16,Fthe UK's defence and I am
OL,17,Fappreciative, and deeply proud of, our
OL,18,Fservice personnel.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,F"Their professionalism and bravery are
OL,7,Frightly respected worldwide, and it is
OL,8,Four duty to back them."
OL,10,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,11,Fsaid: "It is for the MoD, as an
OL,12,Femployer, to decide what childcare
OL,13,Fbenefits it provides for those who
OL,14,Fserve.
OL,16,F"Scotland remains the only part of the
OL,17,FUK to offer 1,140 hours a year of
OL,18,Ffunded early learning and childcare to
OL,19,Fall three and four-year-olds and
OL,20,Feligible two-year-olds, backed by #1
OL,21,Fbillion annual investment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]sD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
