PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773979416
OL,3,CNew military childcare scheme to close
OL,4,C'big gap' between Scotland and England
OL,6,F"If families paid for their full
OL,7,Fentitlement themselves, it would cost
OL,8,Fthem more than #6,000 per eligible
OL,9,Fchild per year."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@PO]
